Class SecureFloatConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uw.medhas.mhealthsecurityframework.storage.database.converters.AbstractSecureConverter
      • edu.uw.medhas.mhealthsecurityframework.storage.database.converters.SecureFloatConverter

  • public class SecureFloatConverter
extends AbstractSecureConverter
    This class extends the AbstractSecureConverter class. It contains methods that convert a SecureFloat object to encrypted bytes and vice versa using Android Room framework's TypeConverter annotation.
    Author:
    Medha Srivastava Created on 1/21/19.
